info.author: Moritz Schlarb
info.description:
tw.tinymce3
===========

TinyMCE WYSIWYG rich text editor 3.4.9 for `ToscaWidgets <http://toscawidgets.org>`_.

It uses and bundles the `TinyMCE javascript library from moxiecode <http://www.tinymce.com/>`_

Original credit goes to Alberto Valverde González (albertov).

You can find the `source code repository <https://bitbucket.org/moschlar/tw.tinymce3>`_ on Bitbucket.
